How to Clean Makeup Brushes:1. Run the bristles of brush under warm running water.2. Apply a small amount of gentle shampoo to bristles and work into a light lather.3. title: Manic Panic Supernatural Pressed Powder, Anemic, 0.25 Ounce
description: Manic Panic’s “two-way” foundation smoothes and visibly improves skin tone. This silky smooth pressed powder provides seamless and buildable coverage. Not only does it eliminate shine and control oil, it hides pores, fine lines and minor imperfections. With five colors to choose from, and broad protection from UV rays, its micro fine finish ensures a smooth, even-toned complexion and a flawless application for long wear ability. It can be applied with a wet sponge or dry; the wet sponge provides heavier coverage while the dry allows for a lighter application. Richly formulated with Vitamin E and minerals to nourish and condition this non- comedogenic and oil controlling powder comes in a sleek compact. This ready to travel with compact includes a mirror and Manic panic’s signature silky smooth powder puff. Long wearing color that won’t fade; this amazingly blend able powder is 100% Vegan and cruelty free. So whether you are creating a canvas for a fresh new look or a mid day touch up, rock Manic Panic’s powder foundation with confidence.
